# talim-ai Workflow

Monorepo: `apps/web`, `apps/api`, `packages/types`, `packages/ui`.

- Prefer existing local patterns over new abstractions.
- Use `pnpm` scripts only; no npm/yarn.
- Secrets in Doppler only — never commit `.env`, tokens, or VPS passwords.
- Local: Doppler `dev`. Server/CI: Doppler `prd`.
- Browser config: `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` only.

## Rule routing

Rules apply automatically — **do not ask the user to @ mention them.**

| When you are… | Rule (read from `.cursor/rules/` if not loaded) |
|---------------|------|
| Implementing `docs/plans/*` or `docs/PLANS.md` epics | `docs-plans` (orchestrates the rest) |
| Editing web UI, pages, hooks, stores, `packages/ui` | `web-next-patterns` |
| Editing API routes, services, jobs, Prisma schema | `api-express-prisma` |
| Editing Docker, nginx, deploy workflow, VPS scripts, env template | `infra-deploy` |
| Browser QA, Playwright MCP, talim-vps ops, post-UI verification | `mcp-qa` |

If scope is unclear, read the relevant rule before editing.

## After changes

- UI work → Playwright MCP or `docs/QA.md` smoke test on `http://localhost:3000`
- Deploy/infra → verify `/api/health` locally or at `http://talim-ai.uz/api/health`
